main event: A radar operator at Keesler AFB detected an unidentified target on the radar scope.
interesting points: The radar target was tracked for about 3 minutes before disappearing, The object may have gained altitude causing it to go off radar, A separate report described a round, bright white object traveling at a consistent speed, Witnesses in another report saw a bright amber, orange, and red object moving across the sky for approximately 10 minutes, Multiple different sightings were reported in the vicinity of Keesler AFB.
